    <title>极乐迪斯科的一些截图</title>
    <link href="/2022/06/13/%E6%9E%81%E4%B9%90%E8%BF%AA%E6%96%AF%E7%A7%91%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9B%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE/"/>
    <url>/2022/06/13/%E6%9E%81%E4%B9%90%E8%BF%AA%E6%96%AF%E7%A7%91%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9B%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220509102735_1.jpg"><br>……<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220522000757_1.jpg"><br>“如果那样的话，难道生活不就是*因为*我们的*继续*而变得越来越难吗？”<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220522120812_1.jpg"><br>“是什么杀了你——爱还是康米主义？”<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220522122911_1.jpg"><br>某种不祥的东西。<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220606015443_1.jpg"><br>“这样很好。”<br>“总算能忘记你了，真好。”<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220606033347_1.jpg"><br>“想念一个人是什么感觉？”<br>“很好。也很糟糕。一种能给你带来欢乐的痛苦。”<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220522121640_1.jpg"><br>“你和我出生在尘埃落定之后的时代，晚了千分之一秒。”<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220606040939_1.jpg"><br>“你拥有如此浩瀚又博大的灵魂，而我也将一直，永远回到它身边。”<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220606041010_1.jpg"><br>旧日之物<br>白色哀悼<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607022904_1.jpg"><br>风被四层高的建筑困在了院子里<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607023754_1.jpg"><br>永远地丢失了，就在那最深的海底。<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607031011_1.jpg"><br>这个名字像是一件*礼物*。一件为你准备的礼物——让生活能够继续。<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607130217_1.jpg"><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607130254_1.jpg"><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607130315_1.jpg"><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607130639_1.jpg"><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607130646_1.jpg"><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607130718_1.jpg"><br>懂的都懂<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607033241_1.jpg"><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607132338_1.jpg"><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607132518_1.jpg"><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607150802_1.jpg"><br>Tequila Sunset<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220511000103_1.jpg"><br>《世界上最悲伤的猪》<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607141547_1.jpg"><br>“这一次我们不会失败。”<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607141649_1.jpg"><br>“在黑暗的时代，群星&#x2F;是否也应熄灭？”<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607144242_1.jpg"><br>Disco Elysium<br>No Truce with the Furies<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607144606_1.jpg"><br>“我见过你，我见过你！我见过你跟她在一起——也见过你独自一人的时候。”<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607153828_1.jpg"><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607153915_1.jpg"><br>“我在想从什么时候开始摩天轮也没法让人快乐了。”<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607171219_1.jpg"><br>烈酒永不朽<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607171504_1.jpg"><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607171523_1.jpg"><br>警督相信你。<br>金*真心*相信你。<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607171637_1.jpg"><br>Sunrise, Parabellum<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607173940_1.jpg"><br>“你衣衫褴褛，不停旋转——浩瀚又悲伤。”<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220511161516_1.jpg"><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607174349_1.jpg"><br>Un Jour Je Serai de Retour Prés de Toi<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607175605_1.jpg"><br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607180401_1.jpg"><br>“我们都有开心起来的义务。而且你*会变得*开心起来的。”<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607180537_1.jpg"><br>*旧日之物*<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607180724_1.jpg"><br>这与失败或者成功无关。<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607180813_1.jpg"><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607180940_1.jpg"><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607181038_1.jpg"><br>当她离开这里时，所有道路都会想念她的脚步。<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220511171906_1.jpg"><br>明天见。<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607182032_1.jpg"><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607182134_1.jpg"><br>未来教会你独处，现在教会你恐惧和冷漠。<br>(“So if I can shoot rabbits then I can shoot fascists”)<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607182259_1.jpg"><br>但他现在可以了。<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607182354_1.jpg"><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607182445_1.jpg"><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607182612_1.jpg"><br>他不想看见生活在继续。人们会遗忘。喝酒。欢笑。<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607184424_1.jpg"><br>伊苏林迪的奇迹<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607184536_1.jpg"><br>I exist too.<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607184638_1.jpg"><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607184649_1.jpg"><br>“节肢动物对你产生了一种静默无声而且毫无意义的敬畏。要知道，我们在看着你——当你厌倦的时候，当视觉失去控制的时候。昆虫会一直注视着你。支持你。<br>当你倒下，我们会来鼓舞你，在你身上发芽、宛如旗帜，在你身上开花，在天葬中将你分离。为了纪念你的逝去。”<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220522111729_1.jpg"><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607183008_1.jpg"><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607184748_1.jpg"><br>“Are you the miracle?”<br>“No. You are the miracle.”<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607184802_1.jpg"><br>“我们这次相遇的寓意是：我是一种相对中性的生命形式，而你是极端的，能吞没一切的疯狂。”<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607184909_1.jpg"><br>“我会试试。”<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607185532_1.jpg"><br>“我们是来这里把你的残渣从马路上铲回去的。”<br><br><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607190754_1.jpg"><br><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SunriseParabellum/blog-imgs/main/June%202022/Disco%20Elysium%20screenshot/20220607190809_1.jpg"><br>“春天来了。到时间了。”<br>结束<br><br></p>]]></content>
    
    
